<item>
            <title>[HBASE-9050] HBaseClient#call could hang</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-9050</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In HBaseClient#call, we have&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
    connection.sendParam(call);                 &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// send the parameter
&lt;/span&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;boolean&lt;/span&gt; interrupted = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;;
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//noinspection SynchronizationOnLocalVariableOrMethodParameter
&lt;/span&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;synchronized&lt;/span&gt; (call) {
      &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; (!call.done) {
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; {
          call.wait();                           &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// wait &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; the result&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;sendParam could do nothing if the connection is closed right after the call is added into the queue.  Since the connection is closed, we won&apos;t get any response, therefore, we won&apos;t get any notify call.  So we will keep waiting here for something won&apos;t happen.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
